publicwhip.spmotion: *S2M-1970 Mr Kenny MacAskill: The Edinburgh Voluntary and Community Sector Compact—That the Parliament welcomes the Edinburgh Compact Strategy; recognises the important role of the voluntary and community sector in Edinburgh and throughout Scotland, and congratulates the Compact Partnership and all the partner agencies who are involved in formulating and implementing the compact strategy.

S2M-1970 The Edinburgh Voluntary and Community Sector Compact (lodged on 8 November 2004) Ms Sandra White*, Stewart Stevenson*, Bruce Crawford*, Mr Adam Ingram*, Rosie Kane*, Fiona Hyslop*, Mrs Margaret Ewing*, Michael Matheson*, Rob Gibson*, Brian Adam*, Jackie Baillie*, Alex Neil*, Mike Pringle*
S2M-1970 The Edinburgh Voluntary and Community Sector Compact (lodged on 8 November 2004) Christine Grahame*, Robin Harper*
